00:00:00.095 --> 00:00:01.459
Bulgarian Cuisine and Drinks

00:00:01.883 --> 00:00:03.131
An Explosion of Fragrances

00:00:03.546 --> 00:00:05.490
The Bulgarian national cuisine

00:00:05.795 --> 00:00:07.481
is colorful and diverse,

00:00:07.913 --> 00:00:10.768
with centuries old traditions and recipes,

00:00:11.630 --> 00:00:13.118
transferred from generation to generation,

00:00:13.524 --> 00:00:16.364
in order to remain unchanged
for hundreds of years.

00:00:16.912 --> 00:00:18.872
Typical for the Bulgarian cuisine

00:00:19.648 --> 00:00:21.728
is the simultaneous heat
processing of most of the products

00:00:22.172 --> 00:00:23.853
and the use of
diverse vegetables,

00:00:24.772 --> 00:00:26.403
aromatic and healthy herbs and spices,

00:00:26.636 --> 00:00:28.604
which our land is rich of.

00:00:30.680 --> 00:00:32.416
Thyme, mint, savory and parsley

00:00:32.824 --> 00:00:34.720
are some of the most often used
spices in Bulgaria.

00:00:35.512 --> 00:00:38.124
Local culinary rules

00:00:38.766 --> 00:00:40.621
are observed in the various regions of the country.

00:00:41.088 --> 00:00:45.024
In the Thracian region people prepare

00:00:45.243 --> 00:00:48.170
some of the most delicious banitsas (pastries) in the country.

00:00:48.233 --> 00:00:51.176
Many local dishes
are prepared in clay pots –

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:55.392
for example hotchpotch and casseroles.

00:00:55.999 --> 00:00:58.562
Many delicious meat specialties
are prepared in the Pirin region.

00:00:58.911 --> 00:01:01.564
Among them are: Katino meze, Chomlek,

00:01:02.965 --> 00:01:03.733
Kavarma, and the local type of hotchpotch.

00:01:03.993 --> 00:01:06.961
Here the secret of the delicious
taste is also the spices,

00:01:07.517 --> 00:01:08.629
as many of them are
local herbs, picked during the summer,

00:01:09.197 --> 00:01:12.079
dried and stored with a lot of care.

00:01:12.657 --> 00:01:13.809
The Rhodope cuisine

00:01:14.101 --> 00:01:16.069
is a part of the exceptional
charm of the Rhodope region.

00:01:16.785 --> 00:01:20.911
It is very specific

00:01:22.119 --> 00:01:26.342
and despite the fact that the dishes are prepared
in many parts of the country,

00:01:26.504 --> 00:01:29.444
only here you will find out

00:01:30.170 --> 00:01:32.968
what the authentic Rhodope barbeque is.

00:01:33.495 --> 00:01:34.599
Only here you will taste
the delicious specialty called Patatnik.

00:01:34.839 --> 00:01:37.178
One of the most famous
Bulgarian dishes is the Shopska Salad.

00:01:36.953 --> 00:01:38.714
Despite the fact that its name is related
to the region of Western Bulgaria,

00:01:39.525 --> 00:01:42.174
this salad is popular in the entire country.

00:01:42.466 --> 00:01:45.403
It is prepared easily and fast,

00:01:45.800 --> 00:01:47.679
as a compulsory element of the recipe

00:01:48.952 --> 00:01:51.481
is the white brined cheese.

00:01:51.893 --> 00:01:54.289
Cheese is present on
every Bulgarian table.

00:01:53.898 --> 00:01:56.907
Bulgarian cheeses are white,
with high butter content

00:01:57.591 --> 00:01:58.615
and specific wonderful taste.

00:01:58.939 --> 00:02:01.203
They are used for preparation
of various dishes –

00:02:01.833 --> 00:02:06.396
pastries, cakes, hotchpotches.

00:02:06.937 --> 00:02:08.090
Another famous
Bulgarian product is yogurt.

00:02:08.220 --> 00:02:10.404
It is included in the recipes

00:02:10.831 --> 00:02:13.023
of some of the most favorite local dishes:

00:02:13.390 --> 00:02:17.164
the cold soup - Tarator,
Banitsa, Snezhanka salad, etc.

00:02:17.390 --> 00:02:19.967
Besides being very delicious,

00:02:20.261 --> 00:02:22.870
yogurt is also very good for health.

00:02:23.608 --> 00:02:25.461
Besides the amazing cuisine,
Bulgaria impresses visitors

00:02:26.066 --> 00:02:28.098
with its good traditions
in wine production.

00:02:28.368 --> 00:02:30.221
Wine is an invariable part
of Bulgarian history,

00:02:30.602 --> 00:02:32.268
Bulgarian culture, style of life, and spirit.

00:02:33.301 --> 00:02:36.560
The ancient Thracians,
who were residing on our lands,

00:02:37.236 --> 00:02:39.795
were using wine as an important element

00:02:40.727 --> 00:02:43.942
of religious rituals and as a way

00:02:44.311 --> 00:02:47.445
of establishing a connection with gods.

00:02:48.068 --> 00:02:50.236
Bulgaria conditionally divides
into a few vine and wine regions,

00:02:50.547 --> 00:02:52.411
and each of them have
their specifics and peculiarities.

00:02:52.833 --> 00:02:55.353
Some of the regional brands,
such as Dimyat, Mavrud,

00:02:55.894 --> 00:02:58.886
Gamza and Wide Melnik Vine
have worldwide popularity

00:03:02.074 --> 00:03:05.446
and a lot of admirers in the whole world.

00:03:06.095 --> 00:03:09.671
A lot of admiration in the country is provided to

00:03:10.015 --> 00:03:12.575
the high-alcoholic drink called "Rakiya".

00:03:13.007 --> 00:03:16.727
Its boiling is a local tradition
with deep roots.

00:03:17.701 --> 00:03:19.217
Bulgaria is a country with wonderful
options for gourmet tourism.

00:03:19.334 --> 00:03:22.401
In order to feel the spirit of the country,
you must taste its food,

00:03:22.910 --> 00:03:26.005
complete the taste with
the wonderful local wine

00:03:26.545 --> 00:03:29.170
and create a total memory
created by all the senses.

00:03:29.893 --> 00:03:31.637
Among the catering establishments

00:03:32.142 --> 00:03:34.342
there are world level luxurious
and classy restaurants,

00:03:34.781 --> 00:03:36.337
as well as small cozy
family restaurants and inns,

00:03:36.667 --> 00:03:39.059
which offer culinary delights
for every taste –

00:03:51.293 --> 00:03:52.837
world known culinary specialties

00:03:53.542 --> 00:03:55.742
and local dishes with domestic taste

00:03:56.181 --> 00:03:57.437
prepared by high quality

00:03:58.067 --> 00:04:00.459
local, ecologically clean products.

